.TH "nvme_init_get_features_irq_config" 9 "nvme_init_get_features_irq_config" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_features_irq_config \- Initialize passthru command for Get Features - IRQ Config
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_features_irq_config
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "enum nvme_get_features_sel sel "  ","
.BI "__u16 iv "  ","
.BI "bool cd "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "sel" 12
Select which type of attribute to return,
see \fIenum nvme_get_features_sel\fP
.IP "iv" 12
Interrupt Vector
.IP "cd" 12
Coalescing Disable
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Features command with
FID value NVME_FEAT_FID_IRQ_CONFIG
